/**
 * Spider Oculus features — unit tests.
 *
 * Tests for:
 * - BlockTypeRegistry.list() / SpiderApi.listBlockTypes()
 * - engine-designs tool
 * - block-types tool
 * - /api/spider/config route handler
 * - /api/spider/session-transcript route handler
